com.davidmiguel.gobees.monitoring.algorithm

Class AreaBeesCounterTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.davidmiguel.gobees.monitoring.algorithm.OpenCvBaseTest
      • com.davidmiguel.gobees.monitoring.algorithm.AreaBeesCounterTest

  • public class AreaBeesCounterTest
extends OpenCvBaseTest
    Integration test of the bee counter algorithm. It calculates the relative error of the algorithm by using the manually counted frames. This relative error is asserted with a max. error threshold.
